element.name: Ballawley Park by kazidrat, Traditional Cache (1/1.5)

description.p: A short walk through a small park.....

long-description.p: A traditional cache, which is hidden in a nice park next to Dundrum Shopping Centre in South Dublin.The cache is a small container in a black sack with logbook, pencil and some goodies . Please rehide it well to prevent many muggles from discovering it.
